OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780304989
OL,3,CIsraeli forces seize strategic castle
OL,4,Cin deepest push into Lebanon for 26
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FIsraeli troops have captured a
OL,8,Fstrategic castle in southern Lebanon
OL,9,Fin their deepest incursion into the
OL,10,Fcountry in more than 25 years, despite
OL,11,Fan ongoing ceasefire.
OL,13,FThe capture of the Crusader-built
OL,14,FBeaufort Castle near the city of
OL,15,FNabatiyeh came after days of intense
OL,16,Ffighting and airstrikes in nearby
OL,17,Fvillages.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
