PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780304989
OL,3,CIsraeli forces seize strategic castle
OL,4,Cin deepest push into Lebanon for 26
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FThe move came despite a nominal
OL,8,Fceasefire that has been in place since
OL,9,FApril 17 and just days before the next
OL,10,Fround of talks at the US State
OL,11,FDepartment on June 2 and 3.
OL,13,FIsrael's Defence Minister Israel Katz
OL,14,Fwrote on X that troops had raised an
OL,15,FIsraeli flag over the castle. Israeli
OL,16,Ftroops previously captured the castle
OL,17,Fin 1982 and held it until they
OL,18,Fwithdrew from Lebanon in 2000.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780304989
OL,3,CIsraeli forces seize strategic castle
OL,4,Cin deepest push into Lebanon for 26
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FThe Israeli military said in a
OL,8,Fstatement that it launched an
OL,9,Foperation a few days ago in the
OL,10,FBeaufort Ridge and the Suluki valley
OL,11,Ffurther south with the aim of
OL,12,Fdismantling Hezbollah infrastructure
OL,13,Fand removing "direct threats to
OL,14,FIsraeli civilians."
OL,16,FThe statement said the army is ready
OL,17,F"to expand the operation if needed."
OL,26,@vD@SO]yD@AOUyD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
