FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780304989
OL,3,CIsraeli forces seize strategic castle
OL,4,Cin deepest push into Lebanon for 26
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FIn recent days, Israel has expanded
OL,8,Fthe scope of its operations in
OL,9,FLebanon, sending troops across the
OL,10,FLitani River, which previously served
OL,11,Fas a de facto boundary, and demanding
OL,12,Fthat residents leave much of southern
OL,13,FLebanon.
OL,15,FIsrael has designated the area between
OL,16,Fthe Litani and Zahrani rivers as a
OL,17,Fcombat zone. Some residents have
OL,18,Falready left the area due to the
OL,19,Fintense strikes in recent days, but
OL,20,Fpeople remain in many of the area's
OL,21,Ftowns.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780304989
OL,3,CIsraeli forces seize strategic castle
OL,4,Cin deepest push into Lebanon for 26
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FThe IDF are now about three miles from
OL,8,Fthe city of Nabatiyeh, a major centre
OL,9,Fin southern Lebanon, and have called
OL,10,Fon all its residents to leave, as well
OL,11,Fas the residents of the coastal city
OL,12,Fof Tyre, the country's fourth-largest
OL,13,Fcity, and its surroundings.
OL,15,FOvernight, Hezbollah claimed two
OL,16,Fattacks targeting Israeli troops and a
OL,17,FMerkava tank in the southwestern town
OL,18,Fof Bayada near the border.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780304989
OL,3,CIsraeli forces seize strategic castle
OL,4,Cin deepest push into Lebanon for 26
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FIn recent days, the group has said it
OL,8,Fhas clashed with Israeli troops in
OL,9,Fseveral towns just north of the river
OL,10,Fnear Nabatiyeh and the castle.
OL,12,FThe latest Israel-Hezbollah war began
OL,13,Fon March 2, when Hezbollah fired
OL,14,Frockets into northern Israel two days
OL,15,Fafter the US and Israel attacked its
OL,16,Fmain backer, Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
