PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1780304989
OL,3,CIsraeli forces seize strategic castle
OL,4,Cin deepest push into Lebanon for 26
OL,5,Cyears
OL,7,FIsrael has since launched a ground
OL,8,Finvasion, capturing dozens of Lebanese
OL,9,Fvillages and towns close to the
OL,10,Fborder. At least 3,350 people have
OL,11,Fbeen killed in the fighting in Lebanon
OL,12,Fand more than 1 million people
OL,13,Fdisplaced.
OL,15,FAccording to Israeli Prime Minister
OL,16,FBenjamin Netanyahu's office, 25
OL,17,FIsraeli soldiers and a defence
OL,18,Fcontractor have been killed in or near
OL,19,Fsouthern Lebanon and two civilians
OL,20,Fhave been killed in northern Israel,
OL,21,Fthe vast majority by drones.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
